_sText:
A classic rendition of zm lila panic


Background:
This map is a built from scratch version of zm lila panic that introduces many new elements to the classic style. For one the map has a newer theme and newer gameplay features. The underground allows for more camping spots and areas to hide out of plain site.

Support:
Cubemaps, FPS (Hints/Skips, Area Protals,Func_occluder), Spawnpoints 64, Skybox
